        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Currently offering a 2 bedroom 1 1/2 bath for $2595! Hurry and catch this amazing deal! We are proud to offer discounts to our First Responders: Active-Duty Military, Police Officers, Nurses. Doctors and Teachers. Call us today to find out more and to schedule a tour. This is a 2 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath, Approximately 882 Sq. Ft. Use this link for more information: https://tower.myrentmail.com/o8jy1i Call Now - show contact info x 144 OR Text 144 to show contact info for more information. Renovated Gated Community Community Info: Mala Grove Townhomes, newly renovated apartments for rent in Waipahu - are available in 2- and 3-bedroom floor plans. These apartments offer attractive wood-inspired flooring in kitchen and living areas, while bedrooms feature plush carpeting. Air conditioning and ceiling fans are available in every residence. As a resident of Mala Grove Townhomes, you have access to an array of fine amenities. Work up a sweat and keep in shape at the fully equipped fitness center. If you have a dog, regular visits to the bark park may develop into enjoyable meetups between human and canine friends. Welcome to our easygoing, pet-friendly community! Discover all the amenities we have to offer. Features: ‣  Extra Storage space ‣  Fenced Backyard on selected units ‣  Expansive bedrooms ‣  A/C, Ceiling fans ‣  Back Door Porch, Entry Screen Doors ‣  Wood inspired flooring ‣  A Must See ‣  Newly Renovated Townhomes ‣  Energy efficient appliances Community Amenities: ‣  On Property Laundry Facility ‣  Fitness Center ‣  Pet friendly with a Dog park ‣  Privately gated community ‣  Swimming Pool ‣  Tour Today ‣  Online payments accepted Pet Policy: We would love to meet your pets! Income Requirements: 2.5 Times the Base Rent Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 9:00AM-4:00PM Mala Grove Townhomes 94-207 Waipahu St., Waipahu, HI, 96797 Equal Housing Opportunity 7u6azcPIUh0",
