        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Two storey house with twelve bedrooms (7 on the second floor & 5 on the ground floor) and four shower rooms and toilets( 2 in the second floor and 2 in the ground floor). It is one of the 3 houses in a gated property . There is alloted 3 free parking for the front house tenants only. Some bedrooms have c at least one chiropractic twin bed /bedroom, a side table and dresser. Kitchen and dining/living room are in the ground floor. The rent is $4,500 / month for a family of six or more. Must have housing allowance as in active military personnel or must have good disposable income to pay the rent and still have some money left for personal expenses. A non refundable application and processing fee of $35/adult applicant is required . Renter's insurance is needed to complete the rental agreement. NO SMOKING & NO DRUGS INSIDE THE BUILDING AND ITS PREMISES ANYTIME. STRICTLY NO PETS NOT EVEN AS A VISITOR. Refrigerator and gas range are provided. Utilities ( water, gas & electricity ) are paid by tenants. Price is negotiable for a family of four people.",
