        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post - This is a great, convenient location walking distance to Ala moana mall, beach, Waikiki, Don Quijote etc. Great for people who work in the Ala Moana/Waikiki area and don't need a car. Great for roommates! - Near buslines and walking distance to anywhere in Waikiki/Ala Moana mall and beach - Walking distance to Ala Moana shopping mall, supermarkets (Don Quijote) and restaurants. - Behind is the Ala Wai canal and is great for biking and walking your pets. - Water/sewer included. Tenant pays electric, internet - Coin op washer/dryer on site -Pets OK (preferably small dog or cat under 25 lbs (but negotiable if you provide pic), maximum 1 pet, additional $35/month for pet) - No smoking inside unit - Maximum occupancy 3 people - Minimum 6 months lease to start then month to month after Available now! If interested, please text show contact info . No application fee. I prefer if you text me so I can reply to you faster. In your first text please include your name, what you do for a living, how many people/pets, and when you are looking to move. We check rental history",
