        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 2 bedroom, 2nd floor walkup apartment. 2 balconies for plenty of storage. You will have your own stairs to your unit, no sharing. 1 parking spot included.This unit is in a very convenient location if you and roommate are attending UH Manoa as its a 1 min walk to the swimming pool/Stan Sheriff center. One pet (dog or cat is ok) but there is a pet fee of $35/month. Walking distance to a lot of food places and easy access to bus lines. -coin operated washer/dryer nearby -Tenant pays electric and internet No smoking inside unit Available now! If interested, please text 8zero8 3eight7 0six2eight thanks! In your first text, please include a short bio: what you do, how many people/pets, and when you can move in. We check rental history. I prefer texting as I can't pick up the often so please text me for a faster reply thanks!",
