        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Luxury on a budget! This is a move that you won't regret!! This is the ideal luxury residence for the discerning person. Fully furnished and ready to move in. The beautiful black marble floors are a start to remind you how beautiful nature is. Welcome to your home in a resort-like setting, in this new, luxury, 3/2, covered lanai, central A/C, and W/D. The best thing is that it is all one level-no nasty stairs to climb up and down daily. Get your exercise on the golf course, not on the stairs! The furnishing and decor is modern, executive black and white. The room is ideal for one person, has a shared bath and is furnished with a double bed, mini fridge, large tv and night table. The kitchen is fully equipped with all major appliances, including a dishwasher, ice maker, and microwave and has beautiful silver Corian countertops. The community center is across the street with its own private pool, spa with Jacuzzi, BBQ. The streets are a runner's paradise with perfectly manicured landscaping. The location is perfect, situated on a corner (there is just one neighbor on one side) just a few blocks after entering Ocean Pointe. You're not on a busy road, yet there is no need to drive through a maze to get home. The bus is within walking distance, as well as shops and restaurants. The beach is just 5 minutes away and the famous Ko Olina resort is just 20 minutes away! Don't worry about parking, there are numerous parking stalls for your guests, as well as street parking. Monthly rent is $985+GE tax. Electricity and water/sewage are shared among the tenants and there is a monthly charge of approx. $145 for maid, gardening, internet, exterminator service. The minimum lease term is 6 months. Sorry, no pets or smoking allowed. Please don't write asking if this is available, I promise I will remove this posting right away when the room is rented.",
