        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Move in special! Reduced rent on selected units. Bedrooms:  1 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  460 Rent Price:  1860 Our apartment homes are located between Ala Moana and Waikiki. Our neighborhood puts you close to all life's needs. Enjoy the exciting Waikiki night life or relax at beautiful Ala Moana Beach Park. Close to public transportation and easy freeway access. A variety of eateries, shopping and entertainment are just moments from your front door. We love your pets! We allow 2 pets per household with NO weight limit! Breed restrictions do apply - please contact us for further detail. Amenities Include: Ceiling Fan Lush Landscaping Refrigerator On-Site Maintenance Convenient Location Gas Stove Bike Racks Courtyard and Dog Park Vinyl Plank Hardwood Flooring Public Transportation nearby Parking Available On-Site Management Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/qgogiogh/moana-vista-apartments **Please note: The leasing office for this property is shared by multiple properties in the area and may not be on site at this exact property. Pricing and availability are subject to change.",
