        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 2 Square Feet: 1044 Use this link for more info: https://greystar.leasehomenow.com/buoq29 Exceptional Island Living Call Now - show contact info x 195 OR Text 195 to show contact info to text us.   Total Monthly Leasing Price (TMLP) $3,988.39 (12-month lease) Community Info Sophisticated living is core to The Element lifestyle. We’re one of West O‘ahu’s newest and most stunning communities, and it shows as we consistently provide the highest quality finishes and incredible comforts to enhance your modern island lifestyle. From our expansive two-story fitness center to our elegant kitchens, when you visit this upscale Ewa Beach community, you’ll see that The Element has the best to offer in elevated island living. Sink into a cozy cabana beside our picture-perfect pool, entertain friends at one of our picnic areas with gas BBQ grills, or take your professional game up a notch in our community Board Room with large screens perfect for video conferencing. Located in the newly developed Ho’opili neighborhood and conveniently close to the freeway for easy adventuring and commuting, it’s truly a new era of phenomenal island living at The Element. Residence Features ✩  Washer & Dryer ✩  Spacious Storage ✩  Energy Efficient Appliances ✩  Modern Finishes ✩  Central Air Conditioning ✩  Private Lanais Community Features ✩  Sparkling Pool With Cabanas ✩  Controlled Building Entry ✩  Two Story Fitness Center ✩  Local Joe's Coffee Shop ✩  Access To Ho'opili Community Amenities ✩  Non-Smoking Community ✩  Convenient Package Lockers ✩  Reserve Parking ✩  Additional Storage Available ✩  Shaded Outdoor Kitchen & BBQ Grills ✩  1G Available Through Hawaiian Telecom ✩  EV Stations ✩  Co-Working Spaces Pet Policy The Element is a pet-friendly paradise in O'ahu, Hawai'i, with no deposit required for cats or dogs. Our monthly per pet fee is $50, with a maximum of two pets allowed per apartment. Certain dog breeds are restricted, including Pit Bull Terriers/Staffordshire Terriers, Rottweilers, Chows, Akitas, Wolf-Hybrids, Alaskan Malamutes, Presa Canarios, and Doberman Pinschers. Further breed restrictions may apply. Please contact us for more information. Income Requirements 2.2 times rent amount Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:30PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Total monthly leasing prices include base rent, all mandatory monthly fees and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable or usage-based fees and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Floor plans are artist’s rendering. All dimensions are approximate. Actual product and specifications may vary in dimension or detail. Not all features are available in every rental home. Prices and availability are subject to change. Base rent is based on monthly frequency. Additional fees may apply, such as but not limited to package delivery, trash, water, amenities, etc. Deposits vary. Please see a representative for details. Equal Housing Opportunity oFKHMY4i",
