        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 1442 Kewalo St, Honolulu, HI 96822 Bedrooms:  0 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  320 Date Available:  2026-07-17 Rent Price:  1510 Welcome home to Kewalo Apartments. Your future community offers studio apartment homes. Kewalo Apartments is conveniently located at 1442 Kewalo Street in lovely Makiki. The property is in a great location just around the corner from tons of restaurants, Target, Walmart, Safeway, Ala Moana Center, and much more. This property is perfect for those who want a central and convenient location but do not want to be right in the hustle and bustle of the city. Makiki is a great desirable residential location comprised of mostly condos, apartment buildings and houses. The property is just a couple blocks from the freeway on-ramp with a small convenience store, cafe, and restaurants. The property features on-site, app-operated laundry facilities. Each apartment has its own private lanai perfect for taking in the fresh air or enjoying your morning coffee. We have a beautifully landscaped property with the serenity of shaded walkways, flowering plants and lush green open spaces. All facilities are maintained by Kewalo Apartments caring and professional staff that are here to meet all your housing needs! I We look forward to providing you with exceptional service that will enhance your living environment every day! Amenities Include: Hardwood inspired plank flooring Balcony AC installation available with fee Public Transportation Bike Racks Built in Microwave Floor to ceiling windows Cable Ready Limited Semi-covered parking Card/ App-operated Laundry machines Full size refrigerator & stove Controlled Access/Gated Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/arex4oer/kewalo **Please note: The leasing office for this property is shared by multiple properties in the area and may not be on site at this exact property.",
