        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 2751 Kapiolani Blvd, Honolulu, HI 96826 Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  830 Rent Price:  2364 Welcome to Waikahe in Honolulu, Hawaii. Our community offers spacious one-, two-, and four-bedroom apartment homes featuring brand-new appliances, full-size refrigerators, ranges (with gas options in select units), hardwood-style flooring, ceiling fans, and energy-efficient lighting, plus we’re pet-friendly! Ideally situated between Kaimuki, Waikiki, Ala Moana, and McCully-Moiliili, you’ll enjoy quick access to outstanding dining, shopping, and neighborhood amenities. With nearby bus lines and the H-1 Freeway, commuting is a breeze. We’re also just minutes from Chaminade University and UH Mānoa. Contact us today to schedule a tour! ProfessionallyManaged by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., HI - License # RB19976 Amenities Include: Elevator (Select Units) Off Street Parking Patio/Balcony Gas Range (Select Units) Refrigerator Laundry Facilities Public Transportation Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/sxxn5jbm/waikahe",
