        "geocode_query": "5100 Iroquois Ave, Ewa Beach",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Kapilina Beach Homes 5100 Iroquois Ave, Ewa Beach, HI, 96076 Call Now - show contact info x 180 OR Text 180 to show contact info to text our team. Use this link for more information: https://greystar.leasehomenow.com/lgtggg Island Living Done Right 4 bedroom | 2.5 bath | 1450 square feet Total Monthly Leasing Price (TMLP) $3,588.07 (13-month lease) Features ✓  Reserved Covered Parking ✓  Spacious Floorplans ✓  Newly Freshened Interiors ✓  Central AC in Select Homes ✓  2-Tone Paint ✓  All New Light Fixtures & Ceiling Fans ✓  Storage Closets ✓  Outdoor Living Area and Backyards ✓  Quartz Countertops in Select Homes ✓  Private Lanais ✓  Full-Size Washer & Dryers ✓  Luxury Vinyl Tile Flooring Community Features ✓  Keiki Pool ✓  6 Playgrounds ✓  D'Lish Restaurant ✓  1 Mile of Secluded Beach ✓  Picnic Areas with Charcoal Grills ✓  Iroquois Point Elementary School, IB World School ✓  Splash Park ✓  Fitness Center / Yoga Room ✓  Active Event Calendar ✓  Gated Access ✓  Beach Park ✓  Volleyball Courts ✓  Walking / Running Trails ✓  Boat Marina ✓  Sparkling Lagoon-styled Pool ✓  Dog Park with Agility Course ✓  Basketball Courts ✓  Hale Clubhouse with Demonstration Kitchen ✓  Iroquois Point Pre-school ✓  Meandering Spa ✓  On-site Evening Market ✓  NEX with Fuel On-site for Military Residents ✓  James Campbell High School District, IB World School ✓  Party Pavilions Community Info Nestled at Iroquois Point in West Oahu amidst pristine lagoons, secluded beaches, and first-class amenities, Kapilina Beach Homes provide everything you crave in island living. The 2-, 3-, and 4-bedroom garden-style rentals feature expansive floor plans, full-size washers and dryers, and ample parking. You will also love that the award-winning Iroquois Point Elementary School is within walking distance. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:30PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Total monthly leasing prices include base rent, all mandatory monthly fees and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable or usage-based fees and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Floor plans are artist’s rendering. All dimensions are approximate. Actual product and specifications may vary in dimension or detail. Not all features are available in every rental home. Prices and availability are subject to change. Base rent is based on monthly frequency. Additional fees may apply, such as but not limited to package delivery, trash, water, amenities, etc. Deposits vary. Please see a representative for details. Equal Housing Opportunity 70RiQFBmvMB",
