        "mainpic": "33ad5653-b161-4ed9-8755-44303d99fda0",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Showings: On Demand By: Linda L. Aganos (R) RB-18827 with Hawaiian Properties, Ltd. Property Address: 98-731 Moanalua Loop #222 Aiea, HI 96701 Enjoy living at Pearlridge Terraces. This apartment consists of approximately 1005 square feet of living space plus a private lanai area and one assigned parking stall. Utilities: Water and sewer is included. WiFi/cable and electricity are at tenant’s expense. There are two community Laundry rooms and a swimming pool. This property is in a great location near the Skyline Rail Station, Pearlridge Shopping Mall and Westridge. The High school is Aiea High, the Intermediate School is Aiea Intermediate and the Elementary school is Pearlridge Elementary. To qualify your credit score should be 670 or higher. And, your income 2.5 times the rental rate. Lease Terms: 1. Available now 2. Minimum 1-year lease 3. $2750/month 4. No pets. 5. Must be a good neighbor and tenant HAWAIIAN PROPERTIES, LTD. For viewing appointment email: Lindaa @ Hawaiianprop.com or phone: show contact info",
