        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Four Bedroom Maili Home Property Address 87-125 Kakalena Street | Waianae, HI 96792 Available: 07/01/2026 Offered By Foster Realty, Inc. | show contact info License No. RB-17493 Description 4-bedroom, 1-bath single-family home in Maili. Set on the Leeward coast, this partly furnished residence offers the comfort of island living. Enjoy your own fully fenced yard—perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding after a beach day. A convenient carport adds everyday ease, while the home’s layout supports comfortable living. Just minutes from beautiful beach parks, local eateries, and essential services like the health center, this location keeps daily needs close while still feeling tucked into a laid-back coastal community. Ko Olina’s resort lagoons and Kapolei’s shopping, dining, and entertainment are only a short drive away. KEY FEATURES: Property Type: Single Family House Bedrooms: 4 Bathrooms: 1.5 LEASE TERMS: No smoking Minimum Lease: 1 year Rental Application Fee: $30 per adult Visit our website to apply or to schedule a showing online at www.foster-realty.com. Details Beds/Baths: 4BD/1.5BA Square Feet: 1,056 Rental Terms Rent: $3,000.00 Available: 07/01/2026 Application Fee: $30.00 Security Deposit: $3,000.00",
