        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post 92-1320 Panana Street Kapolei, HI 96707 Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  635 Rent Price:  2174 Situated on a hill in Makakilo Heights, you will find spectacular views overlooking the west side of Oahu. Here at Cambridge Park Apartments, we offer two and three-bedroom apartment homes with a peaceful and breezy environment. Amenities include an on-site leasing and maintenance team, multiple laundry facilities, BBQ areas, and a gated play yard. We are conveniently located next to Mauka Lani Elementary School and a park. We invite you to contact our leasing office to schedule a tour of our wonderful community at Cambridge Park Apartments.You can also visit our office for more information on Cluster Apartments located at 92-904 Wala'au Place Kapolei, HI 96707. These apartments are all under the City and County of Honolulu Affordable Program, with an 80% Area Median Income Limit. For more information and availability please give our office a call.Professionally Managed by Cirrus Asset Management, Inc., HI - License # RB19976 Available 2 Bedroom 1 Bath 12 month lease only 635 Sq Ft 2 Story Walk Up One Parking Space Assigned Utilities are billed separately for water and sewer Amenities Include: Vinyl Plank Flooring Public Transportation Cable Ready Refrigerator BBQ/Picnic Area Pantry On-Site Management Laundry Facilities On-Site Maintenance Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/iarmkdmc/cambridge-park-and-cluster-park-apartments Pricing and availability are subject to change Equal Housing Opportunity",
