        "location": "761 Wakea St",
        "full_address": "761 Wakea St",
        "locality": "",
        "geocode_query": "761 Wakea St",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 2 Square Feet: 976 Use this link for more info: https://greystar.leasehomenow.com/07p4kw Extraordinary Kapolei 1 Bedroom Call Now - show contact info x 14 OR Text 14 to show contact info to text our team.   Total Monthly Leasing Price (TMLP) $3,654.24 (15-month lease) Community Info Whether you grew up on island, or you have just arrived, Kapolei welcomes all to the sunniest, friendliest corner of Oahu with all the amenities and comforts of the Mainland but with the mindset of Hawai'i. Kapolei Lofts, a resort-style community situated in the heart of Kapolei. In the evenings, you jaunt over to Kapolei Commons for a gourmet dinner and movie. On the weekends you toy with which of the dozens of picture-perfect beaches to lounge at, or maybe you hit the links at Kapolei Golf Club. The kids can play the day away at Kapolei Regional Park (just a few blocks) or celebrate the constant summer weather at Wet & Wild water park. When family and friends visit, Disney's Aulani and the Four Seasons resorts are minutes away from them. And for those days you just want a quiet coffee and a good book, you are mere steps from a Coffee Bean & Tea Leaf. But most importantly, after a long day of work, you can rest assured that you will instantly relax at your resort-style community. Float the day away in our massive pool, or get heart-healthy in our state-of-the-art fitness center. This is your home. You deserve to be spoiled. Residence Features ✩  Kitchen Island ✩  ADA Modified Units Available ✩  WiFi and Cable TV Ready ✩  Microwave ✩  Spacious Modern Kitchen ✩  Outdoor Patio ✩  Walk-In Closets ✩  Black or Stainless-Steel Appliances ✩  Washer & Dryer in unit ✩  Granite Countertops ✩  Ceiling Fans in Living Room and Bedrooms ✩  Central Air Conditioning Community Features ✩  On-Site Maintenance Team ✩  Outdoor Grilling Area ✩  Resort-Style Pool and Sundeck featuring Private Cabanas ✩  Courtesy Patrol ✩  Free Wi-Fi in Common Areas ✩  Self-Service Pet Spa ✩  On-Site Management ✩  Controlled Access Entry ✩  Private Garages & Carports available ✩  Electric Vehicle Charging Stations ✩  State-of-the-Art Fitness Center ✩  Bus Stop just steps from the property Pet Policy Pets - Max 2 allowed, Rent $50 each, Comments: Breed Restrictions Apply Income Requirements Market & Affordable Minimum Income: 2.25 Times Monthly Rent Affordable Units Maximum Income: 80% Program & 140% Program https://dbedt.hawaii.gov/hhfdc/files/2018/04/2018-HUD-Income-Limits-All-Counties.pdf Driving Directions From Honolulu: Take Exit 2 from H1. Take Wakea Street offramp Left into the property 761 Wakea Street Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:30PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Total monthly leasing prices include base rent, all mandatory monthly fees and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable or usage-based fees and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Floor plans are artist’s rendering. All dimensions are approximate. Actual product and specifications may vary in dimension or detail. Not all features are available in every rental home. Prices and availability are subject to change. Base rent is based on monthly frequency. Additional fees may apply, such as but not limited to package delivery, trash, water, amenities, etc. Deposits vary. Please see a representative for details. Equal Housing Opportunity h6ksaUHdAie",
