        "geocode_query": "00PM Kapilina Beach Homes 5100 Iroquois Ave, Ewa Beach",
        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post This is a 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Approximately 1340 Sq. Ft. Visit This Website to See More: https://greystar.leasehomenow.com/8wdiqq Call Now - show contact info x 179 OR Text 179 to show contact info to contact our leasing team. Island Living Done Right Total Monthly Leasing Price (TMLP) $4,393.64 (14-month lease) Community Info: Nestled at Iroquois Point in West Oahu amidst pristine lagoons, secluded beaches, and first-class amenities, Kapilina Beach Homes provide everything you crave in island living. The 2-, 3-, and 4-bedroom garden-style rentals feature expansive floor plans, full-size washers and dryers, and ample parking. You will also love that the award-winning Iroquois Point Elementary School is within walking distance. Features: ‣  2-Tone Paint ‣  Newly Freshened Interiors ‣  Outdoor Living Area and Backyards ‣  Private Lanais ‣  Central AC in Select Homes ‣  All New Light Fixtures & Ceiling Fans ‣  Full-Size Washer & Dryers ‣  Luxury Vinyl Tile Flooring ‣  Quartz Countertops in Select Homes ‣  Reserved Covered Parking ‣  Spacious Floorplans ‣  Storage Closets Community Amenities: ‣  Boat Marina ‣  Active Event Calendar ‣  Iroquois Point Elementary School, IB World School ‣  D'Lish Restaurant ‣  Meandering Spa ‣  NEX with Fuel On-site for Military Residents ‣  Splash Park ‣  Basketball Courts ‣  Picnic Areas with Charcoal Grills ‣  Party Pavilions ‣  Keiki Pool ‣  Gated Access ‣  Beach Park ‣  6 Playgrounds ‣  Sparkling Lagoon-styled Pool ‣  Dog Park with Agility Course ‣  James Campbell High School District, IB World School ‣  Fitness Center / Yoga Room ‣  On-site Evening Market ‣  Iroquois Point Pre-school ‣  Volleyball Courts ‣  1 Mile of Secluded Beach ‣  Walking / Running Trails ‣  Hale Clubhouse with Demonstration Kitchen Office Hours: Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:30PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Kapilina Beach Homes 5100 Iroquois Ave, Ewa Beach, HI, 96076 Total monthly leasing prices include base rent, all mandatory monthly fees and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable or usage-based fees and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Floor plans are artist’s rendering. All dimensions are approximate. Actual product and specifications may vary in dimension or detail. Not all features are available in every rental home. Prices and availability are subject to change. Base rent is based on monthly frequency. Additional fees may apply, such as but not limited to package delivery, trash, water, amenities, etc. Deposits vary. Please see a representative for details. Equal Housing Opportunity 8h3fhMxO",
