        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Convenient ground floor location for UH students, a 30 second walk to the south entrance (Stan sheriff, football field, swimming pool). 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, 1 parking included. Tenant pays their own electric and internet. Pets OK! Preferably under 20lbs (negotiable if you provide a pic of your pet), no barking, no smells, must be trained. Cat or Dog ok, 1 pet maximum). Additional $35/month per pet Maximum occupancy 2 people No Smoking inside unit Available June 15, 2026 If interested please text show contact info . Please introduce a little about yourself: what you do for a living, how many people will be living here, and when you're looking to move. I prefer texting as I can reply to you faster and can't pickup the phone as often. No application fee but we do check rental history",
