        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Beds: 2 Baths: 1.5 Square Feet: 0 Interested in more information? Visit link below: https://tower.myrentmail.com/t47tbl Renovated Gated Community Call Now - show contact info x 141 OR Text 141 to show contact info to contact our leasing team.   Community Info Mala Grove Townhomes, newly renovated apartments for rent in Waipahu - are available in 2- and 3-bedroom floor plans. These apartments offer attractive wood-inspired flooring in kitchen and living areas, while bedrooms feature plush carpeting. Air conditioning and ceiling fans are available in every residence. As a resident of Mala Grove Townhomes, you have access to an array of fine amenities. Work up a sweat and keep in shape at the fully equipped fitness center. If you have a dog, regular visits to the bark park may develop into enjoyable meetups between human and canine friends. Welcome to our easygoing, pet-friendly community! Discover all the amenities we have to offer. Residence Features ✩  Newly Renovated Townhomes ✩  Fenced Backyard on selected units ✩  Wood inspired flooring ✩  Expansive bedrooms ✩  Back Door Porch, Entry Screen Doors ✩  Extra Storage space ✩  Energy efficient appliances ✩  A/C, Ceiling fans ✩  A Must See Community Features ✩  Online payments accepted ✩  Fitness Center ✩  Tour Today ✩  Swimming Pool ✩  On Property Laundry Facility ✩  Privately gated community ✩  Pet friendly with a Dog park Pet Policy We would love to meet your pets! Income Requirements 2.5 Times the Base Rent Driving Directions From Fort Weaver Rd Head East On Farrington Hwy and Turn Left at Leokane St. then Right on Leowahine St. Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM Saturday: 9:00AM-4:00PM Equal Housing Opportunity UqPkPPg4U3ES",
