        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post Welcome to a golfers paradise! Located on the West side of Oahu, the unit is comprised of 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom, with a private entrance and a kitchenette. This experience provides guests with a comfortable home away from home experience, to unwind and enjoy your tropical get-away on a budget. The unit provides central air conditioning, washer/dryer, ceiling fans in all living spaces, several TVs, Wi-Fi, 2 couches, and kitchenette with microwave and coffeemaker, and other miscellaneous kitchen details for snacking. The famous Koolina lagoons and beaches are located within a 20 minute drive, along with the Koolina Golf Club, and Koolina Center & Station that has shopping and various eateries. We are located near the Disney Aulani Resort, Marriot’s Koolina Beach Club and Four Season Resort. All offering various restaurants, shopping, and spa experiences. Due to health issues of the regular occupant, no animals are allowed. The rent is $1650 plus tax, plus a share of utilities, min 6-month contract.",
