        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Kaaawa Condo 51636 Kamehameha Hwy, 211, Kaaawa, HI 96730 2400.00 / Month 1 BEDROOMS | 1 BATHROOMS Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NDM0MDc5?property=805078&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/51636-kamehameha-hwy-kaaawa-hi-unit-211/bfa66246-8056-4a1a-803e-7ad0d0431cd0?source=craigslist Property Description: Furnished 1 bedroom , 1 bath condo in Makaua Village - JUST BRING YOUR CLOTHES! All brand new furniture (TV's, Household furnishings, coffe maker, microwave, iron etc.) Quick ride to the North Shore & 20 minutes from Kaneohe, great local outdoor living, hiking, etc. Awesome new restaurant next door (Crouching Lion) The condo is about 600 square feet, new flooring, new washer/dryer , 1 reserved parking spot with the option to rent more from property management, great little lanie/patio, on-site pool, great peaceful location that is great for outdoor living including hiking, surfing, etc. Minimum lease term is 90 days. Property Type : Condo Pets : No Pets Allowed Smoking : NO Lease Term : 2400.00 / Month 2000.00 Deposit Lease Length: Contact For Details Available: 06/10/2026 Occupancy Limit: 4 People Utilities Included : Water Garbage Appliances : Garbage Disposal Refrigerator Washer Dryer Range Oven Amenities : Off Street Parking On Site Laundry Swimming Pool Wired For Internet Cable Ready Heating & Cooling : Forced Air None Interested? Fill out this form : https://renter.turbotenant.com/general-prescreener/T3duZXI6NDM0MDc5?property=805078&source=cl Have questions? Contact the Landlord : https://rental.turbotenant.com/p/51636-kamehameha-hwy-kaaawa-hi-unit-211/bfa66246-8056-4a1a-803e-7ad0d0431cd0?source=craigslist",
