        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post I have a one-bedroom mother-in-law suite that I would like to rent to a professional. It has a separate front entrance. It has its own washer and dryer. Street parking is readily available. It has a small kitchenette with a min-fridge, microwave, and coffee maker. Cooking of full meals is not possible and could present fire hazards, so it's best for someone who likes to eat out. It has a full bathroom with plenty of space. The minimum lease term is 6 months. The rent is $1,650 plus tax plus a share of the utilities and covers internet, water, sewage, garbage, electricity, community security, right to join community pool.",
