        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post Enjoy convenient living in highly desirable Lower Wilhelmina within walking distance of the mall, shopping center, grocery stores, and Kaimuki businesses. This updated 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom ground-floor unit is part of a classic, well-maintained house (3 units in house). The unit is freshly painted, cleaned, with new flooring, new kitchen, and available for immediate move-in. Perfect size for one or two people. As this is a ground-floor unit in a house, normal everyday footsteps from the upstairs residents can be heard from time to time. We are looking for an easy-going, responsible, and quiet tenant who won't mind the typical sounds of shared living and will respect the peaceful nature of the property. Rent is $1800/month (Includes Electricity, Water, Sewer, Hot Water) Gas (for range) is not included. No parking on property. Shared laundry on property • Lease Duration: 1-year lease preferred. • Security Deposit: Equivalent to one month's rent. Pet Policy: Pets are negotiable and considered on a case-by-case basis (restrictions on size/breed may apply). Approved pets will require an additional pet deposit. • Policies: No smoking/vaping on the property. • Screening: Credit check, background check, and income verification/references required with application. To Schedule a Showing: If you are interested, please reply via email with a brief introduction of yourself, who would be occupying the unit, your desired move-in date, and your general availability for a viewing. Aloha!",
