        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Luxurious and almost new 1 bedroom/1 bath with 1 covered parking located next to Ala Moana Shopping center and walking distance to the beach! This 24 hr. secured building comes with high end Bosch appliances and Hansgrove fixtures. Split AC in each room and a nice lanai to enjoy the great views! The unit comes with a full sized washer/dryer, quartz countertops, porcelain tiles and the building’s concierge desk will always greet you with a smile! The building’s amenities include a pool, fitness center, theaters, party room and comes with lots of guest parking too! You must see to appreciate! No pets. No smoking. 1 year lease. Includes water, sewer and refuse. Please text Scott @ show contact info . Thank you!",
