        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 451 Nāhua St, Honolulu, HI 96815 Bedrooms:  2 Bathrooms:  1 Square Feet:  786 Rent Price:  3174 All of our apartments offer the latest features and amenities where you will be able to experience the highest levels of quality and luxury. Waikiki is Oahu's most iconic tourist destination, and a diverse and vibrant residential neighborhood. Waikiki has grown from a small community of surfers and artists in the 1960s to an urban neighborhood of high rises after a $100 million initiative in the 1970s. In addition to gorgeous beaches such as Waikiki Beach, Kuhio Beach, Grays Beach, Fort DeRussy Beach and Kahanamoku Beach, Waikiki also includes local attractions Kapiolani Park, Kahanamoku Lagoon, Kuhio Beach Park, and Ala Wai Harbor. Close to the mall and everything else! Bike tours, movies, and more! Amenities Include: 2 Blocks from World Famous Waikiki Beach Bike Racks Refrigerator Community overlooks the Ala Wai Canal Controlled Access/Gated Elevator Washer/Dryer Close to the Best Hotels, Shops, and Restaurants Gated On-Site Garage Parking Dishwasher Oversized Lanai/Balcony Microwave Call: show contact info For more information, visit us at: https://cirrusmgmt.com/pongcdib/napili-towers **Please note: The leasing office for this property is shared by multiple properties in the area and may not be on site at this exact property.",
