        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post The Element 91-3598 Nana Hope Street, Ewa Beach, HI, 96706 Call Now - show contact info x 109 OR Text 109 to show contact info to text with us. See our property details here: https://greystar.leasehomenow.com/7a6ytr Exceptional Island Living 2 bedroom | 1 bath | 954 square feet Total Monthly Leasing Price (TMLP) $3,991.49 (12-month lease) Features ✓  Private Lanais ✓  Central Air Conditioning ✓  Washer & Dryer ✓  Modern Finishes ✓  Energy Efficient Appliances ✓  Spacious Storage Community Features ✓  Additional Storage Available ✓  Sparkling Pool With Cabanas ✓  Shaded Outdoor Kitchen & BBQ Grills ✓  Co-Working Spaces ✓  Local Joe's Coffee Shop ✓  Convenient Package Lockers ✓  Non-Smoking Community ✓  Access To Ho'opili Community Amenities ✓  EV Stations ✓  Reserve Parking ✓  1G Available Through Hawaiian Telecom ✓  Two Story Fitness Center ✓  Controlled Building Entry Community Info Live carefree every day. At The Element, coming home feels like you're on vacation. With impressive finishes and resort-quality amenities, our apartments make it possible to live beyond your expectations. With so much to do in the perfect location, a vibrant new lifestyle awaits. Embrace it. Pet Policy The Element is a pet-friendly paradise in O'ahu, Hawai'i, with no deposit required for cats or dogs. Our monthly per pet fee is $50, with a maximum of two pets allowed per apartment. Certain dog breeds are restricted, including Pit Bull Terriers/Staffordshire Terriers, Rottweilers, Chows, Akitas, Wolf-Hybrids, Alaskan Malamutes, Presa Canarios, and Doberman Pinschers. Further breed restrictions may apply. Please contact us for more information. Income Requirements 2.2 times rent amount Office Hours Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:30PM Saturday: 10:00AM-5:00PM Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM Total monthly leasing prices include base rent, all mandatory monthly fees and any user-selected optional fees. Excludes variable or usage-based fees and required charges due at or prior to move-in or at move-out. Floor plans are artist’s rendering. All dimensions are approximate. Actual product and specifications may vary in dimension or detail. Not all features are available in every rental home. Prices and availability are subject to change. Base rent is based on monthly frequency. Additional fees may apply, such as but not limited to package delivery, trash, water, amenities, etc. Deposits vary. Please see a representative for details. Equal Housing Opportunity HZOZ79Di",
