        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post 2910 Kalei Road UH is literally your backyard! This is a existing legal non-confirming duplex built in 1941 has 2 side by side units. Walking distance to UHM, we are located on the makai/ocean side of Hale Noelani apartments. Located near the busline and H-1 freeway. We are minutes away to Waikiki, Ala Moana, downtown Honolulu and Kaimuki/Waialae/Kapahulu/University. This is our side-by-side duplex, 2 bedroom, 1 bath, 1 parking (possibly 2 parking depending upon the size of your vehicle). Luxury vinyl flooring with refrigerator/freezer, range/oven and window a/c unit. Tenant pays for gas (hot water), electricity, cable tv and telephone, water and sewer (prorated) Sorry, no pets allowed. Sorry, no smoking allowed. Please call or text us to schedule a showing or to inquire about our other units that we may have available. Thank you for viewing our unit. Integrity LLC RB-23109",
