        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post Single person only, gated fenced yard, kitchenette, Upper Manoa Valley / Waikiki views, on bus route, clean, quite, safe neighborhood, shared locking mailbox, private locking surfboard / kayak storage under studio. NO drugs or parties, 1 year min lease, unfurnished, $ 100 utility fee / month includes electric, water, sewer and shared washer and dryer that's in a separate laundry room down stairs ( not coin operated ), cable ready but not included, if you have a pet $ 100 / month / pet fee + $ 100 pet deposit / pet, dogs must be well trained and behave, NO dogs allowed in apt due to hard wood floors, only in fenced yard and covered lanai area adjacent to studio, cats okay inside, if you have a full time work from home office additional $ 100 / month utility fee due to more utility usage, if you have a portable A / C additional $ 100 / month utility fee due to more utility usage ( A / C is not needed in upper Manoa Valley, open windows, cool trade winds and fans are sufficient ), For example, if you leave and go to work or school full time 5 days a week, grand total $800 / month. If you work from home full time and have one pet, grand total $800 / month, NO smoking or e pipe inside apt, outside okay w / ashtray for butts ( the yard is not an ashtray ). Landlord lives on property, but does not bother tenant. Yardmen comes once a month. $800 cleaning / damage deposit not to be used for last month rent. Application, criminal back ground check, credit check ( score 700 + ), copy of current photo ID, one month proof of income ( min $ 3,000 + ), proof of renters insurance, NO bankruptcies or evictions in the past 7 years. NO codes, cons, long distance deals, scams, text need apply, onsite inspection required. available immediately,",
